extendedInfo.description: Enjoy the best puzzle game on your Android Phone.How you take off has nothing to do with how high you will fly.Famous iPhone/iPad app now released androidJoin more than 1 million users all over the world.War has started and you are on a critical mission to guard your warship that is carrying all major air-crafts, tanks, missiles and rocket launchers etc.Flight Deck is blocked and now you cant take off, so clear the deck to unleash your fighter jet to destroy the enemy base and save the ship from coming missiles.Relax mode: You will have enough time to clear the deck for the take off.Challenge Mode: You will not have much time to clear the deck.Enemy will fire the missiles in a target time so you must clear the deck so jet can take off.Features:* 2 mode: Relax and challenge* Unique levels* Extreme Fun.* Easy and hard levels* Record time and moves for each level of both mode* Highly addictive* Setting to adjust the volume if each and every component   of game.* Wonderful theme of Navy warship* All levels are unlocked play any level you wish.* Resume from game from the last played level.* Compatible on all Android devices with screen resolution    size 240X320, 320X480, 480X800, 480X854, 1024X600, 1280X720, 1280X800 pixels.* Compatible on Google Nexus 7 phone and tablet,Galaxy S2,Galaxy S3 and other similar devices.In order to give you a free app and keep developing more free apps in the future, we are integrating a search tool to our application. This will add a few access points to your device (hence the permissions) to direct you to the web search service. Please consider using the search to help us keep creating apps. You may delete the search icon, bookmark and homepage easily. Thank you.This free app is ad supported and may contain ads in the notification tray and/or home screen.
